00:16:31.690 --> 00:16:34.402
At any rate, this is
the general form of it.

00:16:34.402 --> 00:16:35.860
And what this
actually tells you is

00:16:35.860 --> 00:16:39.010
that as the energy of
the photon increases,

00:16:39.010 --> 00:16:42.367
the effect of that angle will--

00:16:42.367 --> 00:16:44.700
you guys'll have to work that
