00:17:07.810 --> 00:17:09.790
You've got an electron here.

00:17:09.790 --> 00:17:13.829
What's the probability that
I'm going to scatter off

00:17:13.829 --> 00:17:17.369
into some small area d omega?

00:17:17.369 --> 00:17:25.250
So in some small d theta d
phi, or some small sine theta,

00:17:25.250 --> 00:17:30.012
d theta d phi, into an
