one to one relation

00:18:56.760 --> 00:19:00.570
between the energy and
the angle of scattering,

00:19:00.570 --> 00:19:07.240
which means that let's say
you have a cargo container.

00:19:07.240 --> 00:19:07.740
I'm sorry.

00:19:07.740 --> 00:19:09.600
You don't have a
