00:19:20.960 --> 00:19:21.460
OK.

00:19:21.460 --> 00:19:23.980
In case not, I'm going
to do something dangerous

00:19:23.980 --> 00:19:26.180
and go to the internet.

00:19:26.180 --> 00:19:28.030
And hopefully the search
