00:19:30.820 --> 00:19:32.480
Oh, look at that.

00:19:32.480 --> 00:19:36.230
How about cargo container ship?

00:19:36.230 --> 00:19:37.120
Yeah.

00:19:37.120 --> 00:19:38.330
OK.

00:19:38.330 --> 00:19:41.000
You got one of these, right?

00:19:41.000 --> 00:19:43.340
And your detector
goes off, and it just

00:19:43.340 --> 00:19:45.170
says there is something
radioactive that

00:19:45.170 --> 00:19:46.520
shouldn't be here.

00:19:46.520 --> 00:19:48.110
How do you find
out which container

00:19:48.110 --> 00:19:51.900
it's in without
