00:47:32.230 --> 00:47:35.080
that they do if you add
up the cross-sections

00:47:35.080 --> 00:47:39.850
for photoelectric effect,
Compton scattering, and pair

00:47:39.850 --> 00:47:43.090
production, and you just kind
of bounce on top of those,

00:47:43.090 --> 00:47:45.953
